# JavaScript Function: makeLesson
```javascript
// makeLesson function creates a structured lesson
function makeLesson(topic, level, format) {
    return {
        title: `Lesson: ${topic}`,
        difficulty: level,
        content: `Educational content tailored for ${format}`
    };
}

// Example usage
const lesson = makeLesson('JavaScript Functions', 'Intermediate', 'Text');
console.log(lesson);
```
